{"id":"0d0cc198-cf34-4bab-b7a4-f3af2a12fc33","name":"The Tea Party","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>   The Tea Party from Blue Archive</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Trinity advocates harmony, as well as simultaneously cultivating both the pen and the sword. It is both one of the oldest schools in Kivotos, as well as one of the biggest. The Tea Party is Trinity's student council with it being run in triumvirate-style with the host being swapped between the three leaders in turns. The three leaders of the Tea Party are representatives of the three major factions of Trinity: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 253)\"><strong>Pater</strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">, Filius, and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 242, 175)\"><strong>Sanctus</strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/105040587\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Art</em></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_2663bd5b-126b-466b-beab-86bee826290b.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_bf386089-7908-44e7-a52d-a495770229de.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_d3b818a6-b129-462a-ac1f-29f42d917992.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_939c8509-9ca3-4285-89c7-aa96dc32cef8.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_6c261949-23bf-4bc3-955d-ccd998407f88.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_211f421b-1f9f-4011-b115-44b201a18483.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f4cf1f3d-d629-4937-91f9-5c5a5366dbc4_character-yurizono-seia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 242, 175)\"><strong><em>Yurizono Seia</em></strong></span></a></p><p>Leader of the Sanctus faction. Seia has a distinctive way of speaking as her choice of vocabulary differs quite clearly from the others. Seia is also known to have prophetic dreams which can predict the future and allow her to talk to other people through them. Despite her unusual ability she chooses to not do anything about the dreams since she believes the future can't be changed</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_eca15a08-f305-476f-855a-e417f2443c1a.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_1d96b370-f669-4210-86ed-0f2068f75f0c.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5b5d89f1-7961-4b9f-986f-23cec44f27d4_character-misona-mika\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 253)\"><strong><em>Misona Mika</em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Leader of the Pater faction. Unlike the other two presidents of the Tea Party, she isn't particularly bright when it comes to politics, but her strength is not to be underestimated. She is also a very talkative person, opening disclosing her hate towards Gehenna, Trinity's rival school</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_f5d2cb7","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_65287b44-f720-498b-b3d2-f11199452e26.webp","creator":"FifthBorn","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":2716,"messages":62043,"created_at":"2024-04-13T17:11:50.944482+00:00"}